text: Niecee Nelson is the head women's basketball coach at Fort Wayne since 2016.IPFW's Niecee Nelson makes strong first impression Nelson previously served as an assistant coach at IPFW from 2004–05.IPFW Names Niecee Nelson Women’s Basketball Head Coach She also was an assistant coach for San Diego Toreros women's basketball and as a graduate assistant coach for Wyoming. Nelson graduated from Concordia University in 2002 and University of Wyoming with a Master's degree in 2004. She is married to her husband Steve. ==References== Category:Purdue Fort Wayne Mastodons women's basketball coaches Category:Concordia University (Oregon) alumni Category:University of Wyoming alumni Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:American women's basketball coaches
